snippet.title: The DARK TRUTH behind Johnny Depp's $50 MILLION LAWSUIT!
snippet.description:
Hey guys, today we're looking at the DARK TRUTH behind Johnny Depp's $50 MILLION LAWSUIT!

Johnny Depp is complaining that Hollywood is boycotting him, but a Virginia judge just handed the Minamata star a big win in his $50 million defamation lawsuit against Amber Heard.

Already pursuing $100 million counterclaim, the Aquaman star attempted a Hail Mary move in April to have Fairfax County Chief Judge Penney Azcarate dismiss the two-year old case based on her ex-husband losing a libel trial in the UK late last year against Rupert Murdoch’s The Sun tabloid’s designation of the Oscar nominee as a “wife beater.”
